1
00:01:25,472 --> 00:01:29,792
=Lost You Forever S2=

2
00:01:30,228 --> 00:01:32,880
=Episode 14=

3
00:01:33,738 --> 00:01:35,297
- Are you from Haoling?
- Just die.

4
00:01:42,857 --> 00:01:44,537
You are shameless, heartless,

5
00:01:44,537 --> 00:01:45,537
and despicable.

6
00:01:49,738 --> 00:01:50,818
Our people from Haoling

7
00:01:50,977 --> 00:01:52,857
raised you and taught you skills.

8
00:01:53,617 --> 00:01:54,778
You don't feel grateful

9
00:01:55,217 --> 00:01:56,418
and betray us.

10
00:01:56,977 --> 00:01:58,738
You lead troops to take over
cities in Haoling

11
00:01:58,738 --> 00:01:59,897
and kill our people.

12
00:01:59,897 --> 00:02:00,937
If we had known this,

13
00:02:00,977 --> 00:02:02,537
we would have never raised you.

14
00:02:02,657 --> 00:02:04,178
A dog is even more loyal than you.

15
00:02:07,937 --> 00:02:09,538
And Cang Xuan.

16
00:02:10,258 --> 00:02:11,137
He's also heartless,

17
00:02:11,137 --> 00:02:12,378
sly, and shameless.

18
00:02:12,777 --> 00:02:14,738
Both of you

19
00:02:14,857 --> 00:02:15,818
are shameless.

20
00:02:22,258 --> 00:02:24,378
You can insult me.
Show respect to His Majesty.

21
00:02:24,577 --> 00:02:25,458
No way.

22
00:02:29,297 --> 00:02:30,098
You shrew.

23
00:02:30,098 --> 00:02:30,818
I will insult him.

24
00:02:31,178 --> 00:02:32,217
Cang Xuan is sly,

25
00:02:32,338 --> 00:02:33,697
shameless,

26
00:02:33,777 --> 00:02:34,937
and heartless.

27
00:02:35,098 --> 00:02:35,600
Shut up.

28
00:02:36,178 --> 00:02:37,057
Otherwise, I'll kill you.

29
00:02:37,458 --> 00:02:38,417
Shameless.

30
00:02:38,497 --> 00:02:39,338
Go ahead.

31
00:02:39,538 --> 00:02:40,137
Come on.

32
00:02:41,857 --> 00:02:43,057
Kill me.

33
00:02:43,818 --> 00:02:44,336
You shrew.

34
00:02:44,697 --> 00:02:45,258
Let me go.

35
00:02:46,217 --> 00:02:47,098
I'll tie you up.

36
00:02:54,777 --> 00:02:55,657
Perfect timing.

37
00:02:56,258 --> 00:02:57,057
She's a shrew.

38
00:02:57,458 --> 00:02:58,657
What do we do with her?

39
00:03:02,417 --> 00:03:03,258
Why is it her?

40
00:03:03,297 --> 00:03:04,178
General, you know her?

41
00:03:04,538 --> 00:03:05,378
She is a troublemaker.

42
00:03:10,378 --> 00:03:11,057
Are you alright?

43
00:03:11,258 --> 00:03:11,937
Are you injured?

44
00:03:11,978 --> 00:03:14,217
You deserve to be scolded if you do it.

45
00:03:14,497 --> 00:03:15,458
You lackey.

46
00:03:15,657 --> 00:03:17,258
Just like your master Cang Xuan,

47
00:03:17,338 --> 00:03:18,417
you're heartless,

48
00:03:18,497 --> 00:03:19,378
despicable, and shameless.

49
00:03:19,378 --> 00:03:20,258
Chief Tushan.

50
00:03:20,258 --> 00:03:21,497
Let me gag her.

51
00:03:22,818 --> 00:03:23,538
Yu Jiang.

52
00:03:25,018 --> 00:03:25,657
Bring it on!

53
00:03:30,178 --> 00:03:31,057
What will you do?

54
00:03:31,057 --> 00:03:31,777
Where are you going?

55
00:03:32,458 --> 00:03:33,297
Come back!

56
00:03:34,258 --> 00:03:35,018
Yu Jiang!

57
00:03:35,458 --> 00:03:36,297
Come back!

58
00:03:36,538 --> 00:03:37,338
Yu Jiang!

59
00:03:37,458 --> 00:03:38,697
I haven't finished scolding yet.

60
00:03:39,098 --> 00:03:39,937
Stop.

61
00:03:40,777 --> 00:03:41,538
Yu Jiang!

62
00:03:41,538 --> 00:03:43,178
Are you going out just like this?

63
00:03:52,378 --> 00:03:53,657
Look at where you are.

64
00:03:54,098 --> 00:03:55,417
This is Xiyan's military camp.

65
00:03:55,417 --> 00:03:56,538
There are men everywhere.

66
00:03:56,657 --> 00:03:57,978
If you go out just like this,

67
00:03:58,697 --> 00:04:00,137
you will disgrace Haoling.

68
00:04:04,458 --> 00:04:05,297
How about I order someone

69
00:04:05,297 --> 00:04:07,018
to bring you hot water and clean clothes

70
00:04:07,538 --> 00:04:08,697
to let you freshen up

71
00:04:08,697 --> 00:04:09,738
before you curse at them?

72
00:04:10,618 --> 00:04:11,777
After all, Yu Jiang can't escape.

73
00:04:12,618 --> 00:04:13,338
Alright then.

74
00:04:19,297 --> 00:04:21,137
When I catch that bad guy, Yu Jiang,

75
00:04:21,658 --> 00:04:22,377
I will kill him.

76
00:04:24,257 --> 00:04:24,817
Nian.

77
00:04:25,738 --> 00:04:26,297
Nian.

78
00:04:27,498 --> 00:04:28,377
Are you alright?

79
00:04:32,218 --> 00:04:33,218
Are you injured?

80
00:04:34,257 --> 00:04:35,137
Tell me.

81
00:04:37,257 --> 00:04:38,257
Cang Xuan.

82
00:05:01,218 --> 00:05:02,058
Are you scared?

83
00:05:04,058 --> 00:05:05,857
How could Master allow you to run out?

84
00:05:07,297 --> 00:05:08,817
Let me send you back
to Wushen Mountain, okay?

85
00:05:12,857 --> 00:05:13,424
Xuan.

86
00:05:13,938 --> 00:05:15,218
Please.

87
00:05:16,297 --> 00:05:18,178
Can you please stop attacking Haoling?

88
00:05:18,738 --> 00:05:20,018
My father truly suffers.

89
00:05:20,178 --> 00:05:21,697
His hair has turned white now.

90
00:05:21,697 --> 00:05:23,097
And his health is getting worse.

91
00:05:23,498 --> 00:05:25,218
He even can't walk now.

92
00:05:26,778 --> 00:05:27,338
Xuan.

93
00:05:27,778 --> 00:05:28,938
Xuan, I'm begging you.

94
00:05:28,977 --> 00:05:29,857
Please.

95
00:05:29,898 --> 00:05:31,377
I'm begging you.

96
00:05:31,938 --> 00:05:32,977
You used to promise me

97
00:05:32,977 --> 00:05:34,778
anything, didn't you?

98
00:05:34,832 --> 00:05:35,344
This time,

99
00:05:36,097 --> 00:05:37,618
can you promise me again?

100
00:05:39,458 --> 00:05:40,080
Xuan.

101
00:05:42,938 --> 00:05:43,577
Nian.

102
00:05:44,658 --> 00:05:46,498
This time, I cannot promise you.

103
00:05:51,817 --> 00:05:52,857
If Xiaoyao is the daughter

104
00:05:53,218 --> 00:05:54,178
of my father,

105
00:05:54,577 --> 00:05:55,738
and she begs you,

106
00:05:55,738 --> 00:05:56,697
will you also refuse?

107
00:05:57,498 --> 00:05:59,697
Ten years ago, Xiaoyao pleaded with me.

108
00:05:59,938 --> 00:06:01,458
I made this decision

109
00:06:01,458 --> 00:06:02,297
as the ruler of a nation.

110
00:06:02,297 --> 00:06:03,218
I will never change it

111
00:06:03,218 --> 00:06:04,417
because of you

112
00:06:04,857 --> 00:06:05,857
or Xiaoyao.

113
00:06:47,658 --> 00:06:48,297
Nian.

114
00:06:51,137 --> 00:06:52,417
I know you will hate me.

115
00:06:52,417 --> 00:06:54,178
I also know that it sounds hypocritical.

116
00:06:54,377 --> 00:06:55,938
But this is truly what I thought.

117
00:06:57,137 --> 00:06:58,697
Some matters concern the Xiyan Kingdom

118
00:06:58,697 --> 00:07:00,537
and the Haoling Kingdom.

119
00:07:01,417 --> 00:07:02,377
Some matters concern me

120
00:07:02,377 --> 00:07:04,058
and your father.

121
00:07:04,377 --> 00:07:05,738
But for me,

122
00:07:05,898 --> 00:07:07,338
you are still Nian.

123
00:07:08,458 --> 00:07:10,697
And I am still your brother.

124
00:07:11,377 --> 00:07:13,778
I can promise you anything

125
00:07:14,977 --> 00:07:16,498
if it doesn't
involve the national interest.

126
00:08:06,058 --> 00:08:06,857
You liar.

127
00:08:08,458 --> 00:08:09,257
What are you looking at?

128
00:08:09,857 --> 00:08:10,977
You're just like Cang Xuan.

129
00:08:11,338 --> 00:08:12,817
Both of you are heartless liars.

130
00:08:13,618 --> 00:08:14,417
I hate you both.

131
00:08:17,218 --> 00:08:17,977
I'm sorry.

132
00:08:19,697 --> 00:08:20,938
When I found out

133
00:08:20,938 --> 00:08:22,257
Cang Xuan was going to attack Haoling,

134
00:08:23,018 --> 00:08:24,458
the war had already started.

135
00:08:25,458 --> 00:08:27,018
I had a big fight with him

136
00:08:27,257 --> 00:08:28,297
and even hurt him.

137
00:08:29,658 --> 00:08:31,498
But he still didn't change his mind.

138
00:08:36,538 --> 00:08:38,298
Did you really plead with him
for Haoling?

139
00:08:38,697 --> 00:08:39,497
I did.

140
00:08:40,257 --> 00:08:41,937
And we've in a silent standoff
for a while.

141
00:08:46,377 --> 00:08:47,937
I never deceived you

142
00:08:48,057 --> 00:08:49,298
into treating me as your sister.

143
00:08:52,338 --> 00:08:54,418
I truly wanted to be your sister.

144
00:08:55,257 --> 00:08:56,057
But...

145
00:08:58,817 --> 00:08:59,497
But what?

146
00:09:00,018 --> 00:09:01,257
Back then,

147
00:09:02,018 --> 00:09:02,658
I didn't know

148
00:09:02,658 --> 00:09:04,418
my biological father was Chi Chen.

149
00:09:05,538 --> 00:09:06,577
So after you found out,

150
00:09:06,658 --> 00:09:07,978
you didn't want to be my sister?

151
00:09:09,937 --> 00:09:10,577
Nian.

152
00:09:11,218 --> 00:09:12,377
It's not like that.

153
00:09:13,137 --> 00:09:14,257
The King of Haoling

154
00:09:15,218 --> 00:09:17,218
revoked my clan membership.

155
00:09:18,218 --> 00:09:20,778
He didn't allow me to use Haoling
as my surname anymore.

156
00:09:27,418 --> 00:09:28,978
If you can't come to Wushen Mountain,

157
00:09:29,577 --> 00:09:31,298
at least you should have told me.

158
00:09:35,418 --> 00:09:36,298
I've been waiting for you.

159
00:09:38,577 --> 00:09:39,377
Waiting for me?

160
00:09:39,577 --> 00:09:40,658
Of course.

161
00:09:40,898 --> 00:09:42,418
You promised to teach me to swim,

162
00:09:42,817 --> 00:09:43,898
grill fish for me,

163
00:09:44,057 --> 00:09:45,177
and catch crabs with me.

164
00:09:46,298 --> 00:09:47,218
You liar.

165
00:09:47,538 --> 00:09:48,858
You broke your promise.

166
00:09:51,218 --> 00:09:52,937
So you're angry

167
00:09:53,617 --> 00:09:55,577
because I broke my promise?

168
00:09:58,098 --> 00:10:00,978
I thought it was

169
00:10:01,458 --> 00:10:02,937
because I am Chi Chen's daughter.

170
00:10:02,937 --> 00:10:04,098
What's wrong with that?

171
00:10:04,497 --> 00:10:05,937
Can Chi Chen's daughter deceive others

172
00:10:06,218 --> 00:10:07,257
and break promises?

173
00:10:12,538 --> 00:10:13,257
I'm sorry.

174
00:10:15,937 --> 00:10:16,577
At first,

175
00:10:16,577 --> 00:10:18,218
when I learned of my identity,

176
00:10:19,658 --> 00:10:20,937
I felt desperate.

177
00:10:22,858 --> 00:10:25,098
Everything has been a lie
since I was born.

178
00:10:26,577 --> 00:10:27,697
I knew nothing,

179
00:10:28,497 --> 00:10:29,817
but everyone hated me.

180
00:10:30,538 --> 00:10:31,937
And everyone wanted to kill me.

181
00:10:32,697 --> 00:10:35,137
I really didn't expect you
to wait for me.

182
00:10:36,338 --> 00:10:39,098
I thought you would also look down on me

183
00:10:40,898 --> 00:10:42,057
and not want to see me anymore.

184
00:10:46,418 --> 00:10:47,298
Listen.

185
00:10:47,858 --> 00:10:49,577
Since I've seen you as my sister,

186
00:10:49,858 --> 00:10:51,018
you are my sister

187
00:10:51,018 --> 00:10:51,898
no matter what

188
00:10:52,257 --> 00:10:53,497
your identity is.

189
00:10:56,898 --> 00:10:57,538
So silly.

190
00:10:58,658 --> 00:11:00,098
No wonder you're always bullied.

191
00:11:08,098 --> 00:11:08,978
Right.

192
00:11:10,377 --> 00:11:11,418
I'm so stupid.

193
00:11:11,658 --> 00:11:12,858
Why am I so stupid?

194
00:11:15,418 --> 00:11:16,057
Nian.

195
00:11:16,418 --> 00:11:18,418
Tomorrow, I will cook grilled fish

196
00:11:18,577 --> 00:11:19,778
and crabs for you, okay?

197
00:11:20,018 --> 00:11:21,898
I've also learned new dishes recently.

198
00:11:21,898 --> 00:11:22,937
I'll make them for you.

199
00:11:35,898 --> 00:11:37,298
Nian, it's time to eat.

200
00:11:40,218 --> 00:11:40,858
Nian.

201
00:11:46,577 --> 00:11:47,538
Where is she?

202
00:11:52,658 --> 00:11:53,177
Miss.

203
00:11:53,737 --> 00:11:55,057
The princess has already left.

204
00:12:09,778 --> 00:12:11,018
I missed an appointment once.

205
00:12:11,538 --> 00:12:12,737
You also missed an appointment once.

206
00:12:14,617 --> 00:12:15,617
We are even now.

207
00:12:17,577 --> 00:12:20,418
This is for the best for both of us.

208
00:12:32,400 --> 00:12:35,218
(Haoling's military camp)

209
00:12:35,218 --> 00:12:36,458
You went alone into the enemy camp

210
00:12:36,737 --> 00:12:38,418
and even attempted
to kill their general.

211
00:12:39,177 --> 00:12:40,617
Who emboldened you?

212
00:12:45,497 --> 00:12:46,778
Go back to the Wushen Mountain.

213
00:12:47,377 --> 00:12:48,538
You must not act recklessly again.

214
00:12:57,057 --> 00:12:58,697
Actually, I had the opportunity
to kill Cang Xuan.

215
00:13:00,697 --> 00:13:02,137
He was so close to me,

216
00:13:02,778 --> 00:13:03,978
with no guard against me.

217
00:13:04,898 --> 00:13:05,778
If I had made a move,

218
00:13:06,418 --> 00:13:07,298
I would have killed him.

219
00:13:12,497 --> 00:13:13,697
But back then,

220
00:13:15,458 --> 00:13:17,298
I didn't have such a thought in my mind.

221
00:13:20,617 --> 00:13:21,418
Ru Shou.

222
00:13:23,018 --> 00:13:24,098
Am I really

223
00:13:24,098 --> 00:13:25,377
completely useless

224
00:13:25,937 --> 00:13:27,098
like the ministers said?

225
00:13:39,458 --> 00:13:40,617
You're kind,

226
00:13:41,218 --> 00:13:42,377
not useless.

227
00:13:43,218 --> 00:13:44,778
Don't hear their nonsense.

228
00:13:48,018 --> 00:13:49,257
You can cry if you want to.

229
00:13:59,817 --> 00:14:01,018
I cry out loud

230
00:14:01,658 --> 00:14:03,377
because I know someone loves me.

231
00:14:03,697 --> 00:14:04,697
But now,

232
00:14:05,817 --> 00:14:07,418
Cang Xuan is not here.

233
00:14:08,057 --> 00:14:09,377
And my father is sick.

234
00:14:11,177 --> 00:14:12,617
I should be a bit more sensible

235
00:14:12,937 --> 00:14:14,177
and look after my father.

236
00:14:19,658 --> 00:14:20,497
I can be your brother,

237
00:14:20,497 --> 00:14:21,737
alright?

238
00:14:22,057 --> 00:14:22,577
So,

239
00:14:23,577 --> 00:14:26,177
do you think

240
00:14:26,177 --> 00:14:28,057
I can't take care of you?

241
00:14:29,778 --> 00:14:31,617
Look at me clearly.

242
00:14:32,338 --> 00:14:33,497
Right now,

243
00:14:34,218 --> 00:14:35,137
I am

244
00:14:35,137 --> 00:14:37,418
a powerful general.

245
00:14:38,018 --> 00:14:38,778
I'm formidable,

246
00:14:39,137 --> 00:14:39,778
right?

247
00:14:43,177 --> 00:14:44,778
I know you are very formidable now.

248
00:14:45,218 --> 00:14:46,218
If so,

249
00:14:48,298 --> 00:14:50,177
just forget Cang Xuan.

250
00:14:52,418 --> 00:14:53,497
Okay?

251
00:15:00,497 --> 00:15:01,937
I also want to forget him.

252
00:15:05,538 --> 00:15:06,778
But how?

253
00:15:09,137 --> 00:15:10,257
When I don't know what love is,

254
00:15:10,978 --> 00:15:12,368
I've experienced unrequited love.

255
00:15:13,098 --> 00:15:14,257
When I know what love is,

256
00:15:15,057 --> 00:15:17,817
what I taste is the bitterness.

257
00:15:19,177 --> 00:15:21,057
I thought
I had tasted enough bitterness.

258
00:15:21,937 --> 00:15:23,218
Who knew it went bitter?

259
00:15:37,338 --> 00:15:39,257
Cang Xuan, the bad guy.

260
00:15:41,497 --> 00:15:43,137
Do you think you can get
whatever you want

261
00:15:43,658 --> 00:15:45,898
after being the King of Xiyan?

262
00:15:58,932 --> 00:16:03,280
(Yongzhou)

263
00:16:06,218 --> 00:16:09,177
Xiyan's commanding general is Yu Jiang.

264
00:16:14,538 --> 00:16:15,697
Is anyone willing to go to battle?

265
00:16:15,898 --> 00:16:17,338
- I am.
- I am.

266
00:16:18,658 --> 00:16:19,418
Qing Lian.

267
00:16:21,018 --> 00:16:22,177
Why are you silent?

268
00:16:23,137 --> 00:16:25,057
General, please don't make fun of me.

269
00:16:25,778 --> 00:16:27,098
I've requested several times

270
00:16:27,177 --> 00:16:28,218
to fight against Yu Jiang.

271
00:16:28,497 --> 00:16:29,898
But you always rejected me.

272
00:16:30,298 --> 00:16:31,137
Since you won't send me

273
00:16:31,137 --> 00:16:32,177
to the battlefield,

274
00:16:32,458 --> 00:16:34,658
I have to keep silent.

275
00:16:34,697 --> 00:16:36,137
You will be sent to battle.

276
00:16:37,458 --> 00:16:38,000
What do you say?

277
00:16:40,018 --> 00:16:40,898
I'll accept the command.

278
00:16:40,898 --> 00:16:42,737
You and Yu Jiang grew up together.

279
00:16:42,737 --> 00:16:44,976
You studied and practiced
martial skills with deep feelings.

280
00:16:45,377 --> 00:16:47,057
But on the battlefield,

281
00:16:47,218 --> 00:16:48,497
there must be no friendship.

282
00:16:49,218 --> 00:16:50,057
Do you understand?

283
00:16:50,298 --> 00:16:51,018
Yes, I do.

284
00:16:52,057 --> 00:16:53,697
Yu Jiang was once the pride
of the Xihe Squad.

285
00:16:53,737 --> 00:16:55,018
Everyone took pride in him.

286
00:16:55,338 --> 00:16:56,458
But he betrayed us

287
00:16:56,658 --> 00:16:57,458
to serve Xiyan.

288
00:16:57,458 --> 00:16:58,896
He even led troops to attack Haoling.

289
00:16:59,018 --> 00:17:00,538
He's the shame of the Xihe Squad.

290
00:17:00,697 --> 00:17:01,778
General, trust me.

291
00:17:02,218 --> 00:17:03,817
I will certainly do my utmost

292
