568
00:29:38,857 --> 00:29:40,337
His Majesty has agreed to see you.

569
00:29:40,778 --> 00:29:41,977
Please follow me.

570
00:29:42,497 --> 00:29:43,056
Thank you.

571
00:29:53,658 --> 00:29:54,337
Chief Tushan.

572
00:29:54,617 --> 00:29:55,137
Please.

573
00:30:03,977 --> 00:30:04,617
Why are you here?

574
00:30:05,178 --> 00:30:06,058
I'll go with you.

575
00:30:07,778 --> 00:30:08,658
Are you crazy?

576
00:30:09,178 --> 00:30:11,097
Xiyan is currently at war with Haoling.

577
00:30:11,457 --> 00:30:12,497
As the King of Xiyan,

578
00:30:12,578 --> 00:30:13,938
you'll get yourself killed

579
00:30:14,018 --> 00:30:15,018
in Wushen Mountain.

580
00:30:15,578 --> 00:30:16,457
Hurry back.

581
00:30:17,617 --> 00:30:18,658
I'm already here.

582
00:30:22,938 --> 00:30:24,178
Hide your identity well.

583
00:30:24,778 --> 00:30:26,377
People at the Cheng'en Palace know you.

584
00:30:27,178 --> 00:30:27,818
Alright.

585
00:30:28,018 --> 00:30:29,018
Stop nagging.

586
00:30:29,857 --> 00:30:30,818
I know what to do.

587
00:30:31,298 --> 00:30:32,178
Since I dare to come,

588
00:30:32,337 --> 00:30:34,497
I'm confident I can get back safely.

589
00:30:50,298 --> 00:30:51,097
Heng.

590
00:30:53,178 --> 00:30:53,898
Heng.

591
00:31:00,137 --> 00:31:01,058
Heng.

592
00:31:40,737 --> 00:31:41,264
Your Majesty.

593
00:31:41,778 --> 00:31:42,818
Chief Tushan has arrived.

594
00:31:43,178 --> 00:31:44,058
Did he come alone?

595
00:31:45,457 --> 00:31:47,857
With a male and a female attendant.

596
00:31:50,617 --> 00:31:51,737
Let them in.

597
00:31:52,377 --> 00:31:52,977
Yes.

598
00:32:13,818 --> 00:32:15,938
Greetings, Your Majesty.

599
00:32:16,658 --> 00:32:17,178
No formalities.

600
00:32:23,698 --> 00:32:24,337
Xiaoyao.

601
00:32:26,377 --> 00:32:27,217
Cang Xuan.

602
00:32:38,578 --> 00:32:40,377
Greetings, Master.

603
00:32:49,938 --> 00:32:50,857
Please rise.

604
00:32:57,298 --> 00:32:58,097
Come closer.

605
00:33:11,497 --> 00:33:13,217
I heard that you fainted in the court.

606
00:33:14,058 --> 00:33:15,018
Do you feel better?

607
00:33:15,857 --> 00:33:18,538
I fainted deliberately.

608
00:33:19,097 --> 00:33:19,737
Why?

609
00:33:22,938 --> 00:33:23,857
These days,

610
00:33:24,538 --> 00:33:25,938
I've been plagued by inner demons.

611
00:33:26,778 --> 00:33:28,097
I often dream of Heng.

612
00:33:30,337 --> 00:33:31,137
In my dreams,

613
00:33:32,217 --> 00:33:34,457
her blood splattered in the hall.
She swore by cutting her finger

614
00:33:34,457 --> 00:33:36,058
and begged me
to send troops to save Zhongyi.

615
00:33:37,898 --> 00:33:39,457
I failed to keep promises

616
00:33:39,778 --> 00:33:40,737
and rejected Heng.

617
00:33:42,898 --> 00:33:44,377
Your father died in battle at Mount Xun.

618
00:33:44,737 --> 00:33:46,578
Your mother killed herself
before your father's grave.

619
00:33:50,137 --> 00:33:50,737
Heng

620
00:33:53,137 --> 00:33:54,418
had to lead the troops into battle.

621
00:33:56,298 --> 00:33:56,898
Master.

622
00:33:58,058 --> 00:33:59,337
It's all in the past.

623
00:34:00,018 --> 00:34:01,457
What matters now is your health.

624
00:34:02,857 --> 00:34:03,377
Xiaoyao.

625
00:34:04,778 --> 00:34:07,698
This was where your mother once lived.

626
00:34:08,138 --> 00:34:09,497
You were born in this palace.

627
00:34:10,378 --> 00:34:10,992
Father...

628
00:34:16,578 --> 00:34:17,177
Your Majesty.

629
00:34:17,977 --> 00:34:19,058
Have you always known

630
00:34:19,058 --> 00:34:20,338
I'm Chi Chen's daughter?

631
00:34:21,897 --> 00:34:22,977
Yes, I have.

632
00:34:24,058 --> 00:34:25,618
Don't you hate my mother?

633
00:34:27,138 --> 00:34:28,378
She was your wife.

634
00:34:29,578 --> 00:34:31,818
Yet she had Chi Chen's kid.

635
00:34:33,018 --> 00:34:33,818
Your mother

636
00:34:33,818 --> 00:34:35,417
and father did nothing wrong.

637
00:34:36,298 --> 00:34:37,058
Instead,

638
00:34:38,298 --> 00:34:39,737
I feel guilty about them.

639
00:34:43,058 --> 00:34:44,298
I married your mother

640
00:34:45,298 --> 00:34:47,818
not for love.

641
00:34:49,417 --> 00:34:50,578
Then why did you get engaged?

642
00:34:51,977 --> 00:34:52,737
Back then,

643
00:34:53,578 --> 00:34:54,897
I and Xiyan Qingyang

644
00:34:54,897 --> 00:34:57,378
were both fighting for the position
of crown prince.

645
00:34:58,657 --> 00:34:59,378
It wasn't only

646
00:35:00,138 --> 00:35:01,897
about the engagement
between your mother and me.

647
00:35:02,338 --> 00:35:03,058
It was also

648
00:35:03,618 --> 00:35:05,417
about the alliance
between me and Qingyang.

649
00:35:06,697 --> 00:35:08,217
I never took this marriage

650
00:35:08,217 --> 00:35:09,058
seriously.

651
00:35:10,977 --> 00:35:13,257
Centuries later,
when your mother married me,

652
00:35:14,657 --> 00:35:15,897
she had already fallen for someone.

653
00:35:18,618 --> 00:35:19,138
Chi Chen?

654
00:35:24,497 --> 00:35:25,897
Your mother and I agreed

655
00:35:26,457 --> 00:35:28,578
that we were not a couple but allies.

656
00:35:29,138 --> 00:35:31,058
Once Qingyang
and I were enthroned as kings,

657
00:35:31,338 --> 00:35:33,177
we would divorce and give her freedom.

658
00:35:35,378 --> 00:35:36,048
Sadly,

659
00:35:37,338 --> 00:35:38,778
things went athwart.

660
00:35:39,977 --> 00:35:41,977
Xiyan and Chenrong were at war.

661
00:35:43,778 --> 00:35:44,378
Your mother

662
00:35:46,058 --> 00:35:47,578
had to arm herself for war

663
00:35:47,578 --> 00:35:49,298
and face your father on the battlefield.

664
00:35:55,217 --> 00:35:55,737
Xiaoyao.

665
00:35:57,578 --> 00:35:59,018
Do not blame your parents.

666
00:36:08,858 --> 00:36:09,538
I don't blame them.

667
00:36:13,018 --> 00:36:15,578
If they had no relation to me,

668
00:36:16,897 --> 00:36:18,217
I would definitely admire them.

669
00:36:19,217 --> 00:36:20,257
They died for the country

670
00:36:20,697 --> 00:36:21,657
and the people.

671
00:36:22,858 --> 00:36:24,138
But they are my parents.

672
00:36:25,538 --> 00:36:27,138
They gave birth to me
but did not raise me.

673
00:36:28,457 --> 00:36:30,378
Am I supposed to admire them
for abandoning me?

674
00:36:40,538 --> 00:36:41,217
Over the years,

675
00:36:42,058 --> 00:36:42,897
I have not known

676
00:36:42,897 --> 00:36:44,177
who my biological father was.

677
00:36:46,737 --> 00:36:47,697
Because of them,

678
00:36:47,977 --> 00:36:49,378
I became an abandoned child.

679
00:36:49,897 --> 00:36:50,778
Because of them,

680
00:36:51,257 --> 00:36:52,618
I had to escape from being killed.

681
00:36:53,298 --> 00:36:54,257
I lost my face

682
00:36:54,737 --> 00:36:55,778
and got locked

683
00:36:56,778 --> 00:36:59,058
in a cage like an animal for 30 years.

684
00:37:00,778 --> 00:37:02,098
When I was helpless and alone,

685
00:37:02,138 --> 00:37:03,257
where were they?

686
00:37:04,217 --> 00:37:05,697
When I was humiliated and tortured,

687
00:37:05,697 --> 00:37:06,897
where were they then?

688
00:37:07,098 --> 00:37:08,657
When they died gloriously,

689
00:37:08,657 --> 00:37:09,937
did they ever think of me?

690
00:37:11,138 --> 00:37:12,737
I don't care whether they were a demon

691
00:37:12,737 --> 00:37:13,818
or a heroine.

692
00:37:14,457 --> 00:37:15,338
In my eyes,

693
00:37:16,177 --> 00:37:17,298
they are just

694
00:37:17,298 --> 00:37:18,338
irresponsible people.

695
00:37:18,618 --> 00:37:19,538
They abandoned me.

696
00:37:19,618 --> 00:37:20,657
They're not good parents.

697
00:37:24,138 --> 00:37:24,897
Master.

698
00:37:25,858 --> 00:37:27,378
When they resolutely faced death,

699
00:37:27,378 --> 00:37:28,897
they didn't seek our consent.

700
00:37:29,657 --> 00:37:30,858
Now things have changed.

701
00:37:30,858 --> 00:37:31,697
It's unnecessary

702
00:37:31,697 --> 00:37:32,977
to demand our forgiveness.

703
00:37:46,937 --> 00:37:47,897
I don't blame you.

704
00:37:51,497 --> 00:37:52,098
Xiaoyao.

705
00:37:53,697 --> 00:37:54,977
I want to take you to a place.

706
00:37:59,538 --> 00:38:00,217
What place?

707
00:38:01,497 --> 00:38:02,338
Baili.

708
00:38:03,088 --> 00:38:06,098
(Chi Chen Village, Baili)

709
00:38:06,098 --> 00:38:08,417
Your father and mother
were not often together.

710
00:38:09,018 --> 00:38:10,578
Whenever he missed your mother,

711
00:38:11,018 --> 00:38:12,457
he would plant a peach tree,

712
00:38:13,578 --> 00:38:16,257
watering it with spirit power
amidst the landscape.

713
00:38:16,977 --> 00:38:18,177
After hundreds of years,

714
00:38:18,378 --> 00:38:20,778
the peach trees created a large forest

715
00:38:20,937 --> 00:38:22,177
as a barrier.

716
00:38:24,177 --> 00:38:27,618
After tens of millions of years,
the peach forest in Mount Jade

717
00:38:27,657 --> 00:38:30,217
developed the rare weapon,
Rejuvenating Flower.

718
00:38:30,937 --> 00:38:31,818
When you were born,

719
00:38:32,417 --> 00:38:35,538
your mother risked her life
to seal the Rejuvenating Flower

720
00:38:36,177 --> 00:38:38,177
within you with her blood.

721
00:38:39,217 --> 00:38:40,298
No wonder when I was little,

722
00:38:40,298 --> 00:38:42,098
people said I looked like Your Majesty.

723
00:38:43,058 --> 00:38:44,697
So it was the effect
of the Rejuvenating Flower.

724
00:38:50,298 --> 00:38:52,018
This is your parents' home.

725
00:38:54,538 --> 00:38:55,098
Home?

726
00:39:01,737 --> 00:39:03,977
Your father is the general
in charge of Chenrong.

727
00:39:05,177 --> 00:39:07,257
Your mother is the only disciple
of the Lady Xiezu.

728
00:39:07,818 --> 00:39:09,378
But all they desired

729
00:39:10,378 --> 00:39:11,298
was just

730
00:39:12,697 --> 00:39:13,257
a home.

731
00:39:14,937 --> 00:39:15,697
Xiaoyao.

732
00:39:17,138 --> 00:39:18,338
You are like your mother.

733
00:39:21,417 --> 00:39:22,937
I am content with my destiny.

734
00:39:23,497 --> 00:39:24,778
I only want to live well

735
00:39:25,177 --> 00:39:26,177
without thinking far ahead.

736
00:39:28,098 --> 00:39:29,858
I'll never try to be a heroine.

737
00:39:34,138 --> 00:39:34,937
Just look around.

738
00:39:36,217 --> 00:39:37,378
We'll wait for you outside.

739
00:40:45,457 --> 00:40:46,138
- Xiaoyao.
- Stop.

740
00:40:48,497 --> 00:40:50,338
Chi Chen built this place
for his wife and daughter.

741
00:40:51,138 --> 00:40:52,778
No one can hurt Xiaoyao here.

742
00:41:14,977 --> 00:41:15,578
Who is it?

743
00:41:17,897 --> 00:41:18,457
I'm sorry

744
00:41:19,098 --> 00:41:20,058
I scared you.

745
00:41:24,018 --> 00:41:24,624
Sorry.

746
00:41:25,417 --> 00:41:26,657
I didn't know there was someone else.

747
00:41:26,977 --> 00:41:28,217
I was just shocked.

748
00:41:30,177 --> 00:41:31,457
Who are you?

749
00:41:31,858 --> 00:41:32,432
I...

750
00:41:33,217 --> 00:41:33,897
I am...

751
00:41:38,497 --> 00:41:39,697
The caretaker of the house.

752
00:41:45,538 --> 00:41:46,257
Madam.

753
00:41:46,977 --> 00:41:49,018
The portraits are...

754
00:41:51,578 --> 00:41:52,417
Chi Chen

755
00:41:53,778 --> 00:41:54,977
and Xiling Heng.

756
00:41:55,338 --> 00:41:56,378
Have you ever seen them?

757
00:41:58,538 --> 00:41:59,138
Yes.

758
00:42:03,177 --> 00:42:03,977
Back off.

759
00:42:04,937 --> 00:42:07,618
I was injured on the battlefield.

760
00:42:08,417 --> 00:42:09,257
I can't meet people.

761
00:42:09,618 --> 00:42:10,138
Okay.

762
00:42:10,457 --> 00:42:11,257
I won't go over.

763
00:42:11,497 --> 00:42:12,298
Don't be afraid.

764
00:42:13,858 --> 00:42:15,417
I just want to chat with you.

765
00:42:17,257 --> 00:42:20,138
I'd like to talk about the portraits.

766
00:42:21,937 --> 00:42:22,657
Over here,

767
00:42:24,098 --> 00:42:24,937
Chi Chen

768
00:42:25,538 --> 00:42:26,937
was not

769
00:42:27,657 --> 00:42:28,977
a ruthless demon

770
00:42:30,378 --> 00:42:31,298
that killed people.

771
00:42:32,018 --> 00:42:34,778
He was the King of Beasts,
protecting the Baili,

772
00:42:35,338 --> 00:42:38,457
and being favored by people from Baili.

773
00:42:40,778 --> 00:42:41,818
Xiling Heng

774
00:42:42,977 --> 00:42:43,858
was not

775
00:42:44,417 --> 00:42:45,417
a high-status,

776
00:42:45,778 --> 00:42:49,177
prudent Princess General.

777
00:42:50,217 --> 00:42:52,417
She was simply Chi Chen's wife.

778
00:42:53,098 --> 00:42:54,768
She practiced medicine and saved people

779
00:42:55,497 --> 00:42:57,298
and was revered by the people from Baili

780
00:42:58,138 --> 00:42:59,977
as the Xiling Witch.

781
00:43:19,098 --> 00:43:22,330
♪Looking back on my old days♪

782
00:43:23,616 --> 00:43:27,898
♪I was unruffled
with no sorrow and soreness♪

783
00:43:29,978 --> 00:43:34,778
♪In my chaotic life,
I failed to meet your gaze♪

784
00:43:37,914 --> 00:43:40,186
♪Only emptiness remained♪

785
00:43:43,130 --> 00:43:46,202
♪Enduring all things in my life♪

786
00:43:48,051 --> 00:43:52,442
♪I valued all but indifferent
to wealth and fame♪

787
00:43:53,978 --> 00:43:59,451
♪Basking in the sun,
I couldn't feel your sunlight♪

788
00:44:00,402 --> 00:44:06,234
♪All I feel is a painful heat wave♪

789
00:44:09,082 --> 00:44:13,818
♪All things are dim,
while only your eyes shine bright♪

790
00:44:15,130 --> 00:44:19,642
♪I'll follow my heart
and go to chase the sun far away♪

791
00:44:21,082 --> 00:44:27,034
♪Everything seems sad,
while only your brows raise in delight♪

792
00:44:27,811 --> 00:44:32,122
♪I'm waiting for you
to enjoy the scenery at night♪

793
00:44:33,114 --> 00:44:38,080
♪You came with wind and rain,
while left with my four seasons♪

794
00:44:39,072 --> 00:44:43,680
♪All is bleak without you♪

795
00:44:45,018 --> 00:44:50,624
♪It began like a tornado,
and went away leaving only dust♪

796
00:44:51,738 --> 00:45:02,752
♪Without you,
even the most beautiful world is a mess♪
